Hold! the value is 0
When /someone/ wishes to increment with step /step/ {
    set oldVal [dict get [QueryOne! the value is /val/] val]
    Hold! the value is [+ $oldVal $step]
}

Wish to increment with step 1
sleep 0.05
Wish to increment with step 3
sleep 0.05

assert {[dict get [QueryOne! the value is /val/] val] == 4}

Hold! the value is 0
When /someone/ wishes to increment with /...options/ {
    set oldVal [dict get [QueryOne! the value is /val/] val]
    Hold! the value is [+ $oldVal $options(step)]
}

Wish to increment with step 1
sleep 0.05
Wish to increment with step 3
sleep 0.05

assert {[dict get [QueryOne! the value is /val/] val] == 4}
Exit! 0
